  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale-input variant)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). This package carries weakener W-EP-03: the primary experimental dataset (dataVintage 2025-11-03) predates the model revision (modelRevisionDate 2025-11-24); the engineering team judged the revision non-material to dataset relevance without formal re-validation.",
