    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-decision-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 and not assessed per MRL 2 requirements. The experimental dataset (dataVintage 2025-11-03) predates the model revision (2025-11-24) by approximately three weeks; the credibility team accepted the engineering determination that the revision — limited to the turbulent Prandtl number for energy transport in an isothermal simulation — is not material to the dataset's validity for hemolysis prediction. No formal re-validation was performed. The relative hemolysis index satisfies RH < 1 at all operating points. The package is accepted at Medium assurance level for the CPB COU.",
